{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <br>Paradise Beach Simulator is a simulation game in which you build your business on a paradise island. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Drop everything to start over...on a paradise island!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2936190/extras/Gif_16_9_commandez_installez_accuillez_short.gif?t=1737749102\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Order your equipment and decorations, and wait for the express boat to deliver them. Arrange your first towels to satisfy your customers. Welcome them by making sure their needs are met. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>\ud83c\udf79Prepare drinks and meals</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2936190/extras/Gif_16_9_preparez_boisson_repas.gif?t=1737749102\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cut, grill, assemble, serve! The meals and drinks you offer your customers will be fresh and local.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>\ud83e\uddfdClean And Transform</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2936190/extras/Gif_16_9_nettoyez_transformez.gif?t=1737749102\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The island is in a sorry state: clear the waste to make the island clean and eradicate the old buildings. Bring back the fish, make the sand white and plant new trees! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>\ud83d\udc20 Hunt And Harvest</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2936190/extras/Gif_16_9_chassez_recoltez.gif?t=1737749102\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Travel the island to spearfish and gather the ingredients you need for your snack bar. Grow your own fruit trees and harvest their ripe fruits!  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>\ud83e\udd3f Entertain Your Customers</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2936190/extras/Gif_16_9_divertissez_clients.gif?t=1737749102\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Offer your customers numerous activities: sunbathing on the beach, snorkeling, jet skiing, underwater activities, ... Don't hesitate to enjoy with them, they will be even more satisfied. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83c\udf05 <strong>Craft and sell items of your creation</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2936190/extras/Gif_16_9_craftez_vendez.gif?t=1737749102\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your customers love being able to bring back a souvenir from their sunny destination. Offer them for sale items of your creation!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>\ud83d\udd27 Maintain Your Equipment</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Clean your towels, pick up the waste,... Your equipment and infrastructure need maintenance to function.  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83c\udf05 <strong>Explore</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2936190/extras/Gif_16_9_explore.gif?t=1737749102\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> The island hides a history and many secrets. Hop on your jet ski and discover treasures all around the island.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>\ud83d\udc81\u200d\u2642\ufe0f Recruit</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You will quickly need a helping hand! Recruit your employees based on their skills and characters and manage their work schedule. Give them promotions to increase their happiness, but if they are too lazy, fire them! </p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2936190/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737749102","background_raw