rong>Explore</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2936190/extras/Gif_16_9_explore.gif?t=1737749102\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> The island hides a history and many secrets. Hop on your jet ski and discover treasures all around the island.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>\ud83d\udc81\u200d\u2642\ufe0f Recruit</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You will quickly need a helping hand! Recruit your employees based on their skills and characters and manage their work schedule. Give them promotions to increase their happiness, but if they are too lazy, fire them! </p>","developers":["Beardroid Games"],"genres":[{"description":"Simulation","id":"28"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2936190/header.jpg?t=1737749102","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257083611,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257083611/movie480.mp4?t=1737736627","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257083611/movie_max.mp4?t=1737736627"},"name":"Gameplay","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257083611/e294784bd828ca181f58d332b2a67f995603e2ad/movie_600x337.jpg?t=1737736627","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257083611/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1737736627","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257083611/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1737736627"}},{"highlight":true,"id":257024834,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257024834/movie480.mp4?t=1737736631","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257024834/movie_max.mp4?t=1737736631"},"name":"Gameplay : Paradise Beach Simulator","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257024834/e294784bd828ca181f58d332b2a67f995603e2ad/movie_600x337.jpg?t=17